```plantuml
@startuml darrenyao87_tnn-models

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<TNN>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<HiAI>> LightGreen
}

[TNN Framework] <<TNN>> as TNN
[HiAI DDK] <<HiAI>> as HiAI
[Model Management] as MM
[AI Pre-Processing (AIPP)] as AIPP
[Tensor Handling] as TH
[Neural Network Layers] as NNL
[Object Detection & Classification] as ODC
[OCR] as OCR
[BERT Models] as BERT
[Image Segmentation & Pose Estimation] as ISPE
[Image Translation] as IT
[Hardware Acceleration] as HA

TNN --> MM : Provides
HiAI --> MM : Provides
HiAI --> AIPP : Implements
HiAI --> TH : Manages
TNN --> NNL : Defines
MM --> ODC : Manages
MM --> OCR : Manages
MM --> BERT : Manages
MM --> ISPE : Manages
MM --> IT : Manages
TH --> HA : Utilizes
NNL --> HA : Leverages

database "Model Files" {
  [.tnnproto]
  [.tnnmodel]
  [.rapidproto]
  [.rapidmodel]
  [.onnx]
}

MM --> [Model Files] : Serializes/Deserializes

database "Supporting Data" {
  [vocab.txt]
  [keys.txt]
  [anchors.txt]
}

OCR --> [keys.txt] : Uses
BERT --> [vocab.txt] : Uses
ODC --> [anchors.txt] : Uses

@enduml
```